title: Hostile Waters - Antaeus Rising
description:
One of the best games ever! It's a shame it is almost completely forgotten, it is not for sale anywhere and it is very hard to find a place to download it from.

But here is it! A straight copy of the original disc with the latest patch included and a actually working and clean crack. Please enjoy this missing piece of history in PC-games best time ever! When the games was not all about graphics and physics.


Any computer at least from 2002 can run this game smoothly so i don't think the specs is neccesarily to write down :).
